title: NFL ATL: DeSean reaction, Jeff Darlington in studio!
itunes:title: NFL ATL: DeSean reaction, Jeff Darlington in studio!
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- welcomes NFL Media’s Jeff Darlington to Studio 66 to run through the latest offseason news.  Which free agency moves does he believe will pay dividends?  Is the gang sold on the Washington Redskins’ chances in the NFC East with DeSean Jackson in burgundy and gold?  Tune in and find out.
